---
import UseCase from '../../../UseCase.astro';
import UseCaseInteractive from '../../../UseCaseInteractive.astro';
import Usage from '../../../Usage.astro';
import UsageItem from '../../../UsageItem.astro';
---

<UseCase
  title="Concise, Goal-Oriented AI Output"
  description="Keep AI responses focused on the user's question or task—concise and actionable, without unnecessary preamble, repetition, or tangents."
>
  <UseCaseInteractive clsHeight={112} label="Concise, goal-oriented output" toggle>
    <div class="grid gap-600 w-full">
      <div class="grid gap-400 p-600 rounded-lg bg-tone-neutral-09 border border-tone-neutral-03">
        <div class="grid gap-200">
          <mds-text typography="label"><b>Direct Answer</b></mds-text>
          <mds-text typography="body"
            >Yes. Your refund will be processed in 3–5 business days. Track it in Orders → [Order
            #123].</mds-text
          >
          <mds-text typography="caption" class="text-tone-neutral-05"
            >Answers the question first; one line of next step. No filler.</mds-text
          >
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="grid gap-400 p-600 rounded-lg bg-tone-neutral-09 border border-tone-neutral-03">
        <div class="grid gap-200">
          <mds-text typography="label"><b>Task-Focused Summary</b></mds-text>
          <mds-text typography="body"
            >Here are the 3 changes suggested for your draft: (1) Fix typo in §2. (2) Shorten the
            intro. (3) Add a citation for the claim in §4. [Apply all] [Review one by one]</mds-text
          >
          <mds-text typography="caption" class="text-tone-neutral-05"
            >Numbered, scannable list tied to actions; user can apply or drill in.</mds-text
          >
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="grid gap-400 p-600 rounded-lg bg-status-error-10 border border-status-error-03">
        <div class="grid gap-200">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-200">
            <mds-icon name="mi/outline/error" class="text-status-error-05"></mds-icon>
            <mds-text typography="label"><b>Verbose, Unfocused (Problematic)</b></mds-text>
          </div>
          <mds-text typography="body"
            >"Thank you for asking! Refunds are an important part of our policy. Generally speaking,
            we aim to process refunds as quickly as possible. In your case, after reviewing your
            request, I can confirm that yes, your refund will be processed. Typically this takes 3–5
            business days, though it can vary. You can track your order in the Orders section. Is
            there anything else I can help with?"</mds-text
          >
          <mds-text typography="caption" class="text-status-error-06"
            >Preamble, repetition, and polite filler obscure the answer and next step; wastes time.</mds-text
          >
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </UseCaseInteractive>
  <Usage>
    <UsageItem variant="do">
      Lead with the answer or outcome; keep text short and tied to the user's goal.
    </UsageItem>
    <UsageItem variant="dont">
      Pad responses with long preambles, repeated phrasing, or tangents that don't support the task.
    </UsageItem>
    <UsageItem variant="do">
      Use lists, bullets, or short paragraphs so users can scan and act quickly.
    </UsageItem>
    <UsageItem variant="dont">
      Default to long prose when a few lines or a structured summary would suffice.
    </UsageItem>
  </Usage>
</UseCase>
